name: Graham Combs
short_description:
Outer Banks Grocery Stockers has been in business since 1996. Providing the Outer Banks tourist and locals with top quality service. We will provide all your grocery needs while you are on vacation!! Plus much more, We also have beach rental equipment, Vacation Equipment and Linen service for you vacation needs. Our inventory is extensive and special orders can be made for items not in our inventory. We supply all paper and cleaning products, condiments, drinks, snacks, cooking staples, etc. We deal only with the finest and freshest. We purchase our seafood from local fishermen and supply only Grade A USDA Beef, Poultry and Pork.
Location: 5561 North Croatan Hwy STE 173 Kitty Hawk, North Carolina 27949 United States
